Remove duplicates in sorted array:

Link: https://leetcode.com/problems/rotate-array/

Java Implementation:

class Solution {
    public int removeDuplicates(int[] nums) {
        int j=0;
        for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
            if(nums[j]!=nums[i]){
                nums[++j]=nums[i];
            }
        }
        return j+1;
    }
}
